name: UInterchangeAnimationTrackBaseNode
doc: Abstract class providing the minimal services required for an animation track node.

methods.name: GetCustomCompletionMode
methods.doc:
Get how the actor's animated property behaves once this animation is complete.
The output value will be clamped to the range of values defined in EInterchangeAimationCompletionMode.

methods.name: SetCustomCompletionMode
methods.doc: Set how the actor's animated property should behave once its animation completes.
